  * src/update-notifier.c: Now that we have it, use apport's native icon
    instead of the bomb.
  * Remove pixmaps/16x16/crashreport-notifier.png, obsolete.

 -- Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>  Thu, 22 Feb 2007 13:56:12 +0100

